    "updated_at": "2015-08-24T08:29:13Z",
    "body": "From my point, it's not related to node's require mechanism, instead, this is more like a way of Electron startup. The `package.json` tells your app details(e.g. name, version) and the entry js file location(in `main` field). \n"
